## 2. THE COMMERCIAL PATH: "WORK-OR-PAY" MODEL
For entities generating revenue, commercial studios, or those who wish to keep their modifications private.

To use VibeSync commercially without being subject to the AGPLv3 source-sharing requirements, you must satisfy **ONE** of the following:

### A. Maintenance Contribution (Manpower)
Documented and verified "Significant Maintenance Contributions" to the project (Code, Documentation, Infrastructure).
### B. Commercial License Fee (Money)
Payment of the stipulated commercial license fee.
### C. Explicit Discretionary Waiver
A written waiver granted by the Author at their sole discretion.

