## 3. OPEN-CORE, R&D OPERATIONS & EARLY ACCESS
VibeSync employs an **Open-Core** model. During the active research and development phase, **ALL** Unity ↔ Blender orchestration features—including complex AI and Vision tiers—are provided at **Zero Cost** for public non-commercial use to facilitate community stress-testing.

**TRANSITION POLICY**: Upon v1.0, the Author reserves the right to activate a **Credit-Gate** for advanced, high-compute, or commercial-use operations. This monetization supports continued development of the core bridge. Notice will be provided 30 days prior.

| Operation Tier | Cost (R&D Phase) | Final Tier (v1.0+) |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Unity/Blender Basic Sync** | **Free** | **Free** |
| **Advanced AI/Complex Sync** | **Free** | **Credits Required** |
| **Vision/Audit Tools** | **Free** | **Credits Required** |

**SERVICE COMPLIANCE & LIABILITY**: Users acknowledge that these experimental bridges can cause significant state corruption in Unity and Blender. Use is at the user's sole risk. See Section 5 for full liability limitations.

